description: This two bedroom, one bathroom unit at The Foundry offers a stunning loft-style space with high ceilings and exposed brick and wood beams.  The kitchen cabinets and engineered wood floors are new and unit freshly painted.  Stand out interior features include the master bedroom large walk-in closet, and loft space above the kitchen perfect for a guest bed.  That would allow the second bedroom to be utilized as a great office space for remote workers!  This professionally managed property is pet friendly and handicapped accessible with an elevator.  There is common laundry and bike storage.  Living here also offers quick access to mass transit, many restaurants, shops and cafes!  A quick Uber to the Seaport is very enticing!  First open house this Sunday, April 14th from 1-2:30.
